description:
Wholesale distributors of electrical parts and communications
equipment. Products for sale may include electronic coils, capacitors,
electronic condensers, diodes, semiconductor devices, public address
equipment, and electric signs.
For retailers that sell electronic equipment, use MCC 5732.
For retailers that sell telecommunications equipment such as
telephones and pagers, use MCC 4812.
